to add to git

git init
git status
git add .
git status
git commit -m "my first commit - admin views create"
git log

adding laravelcollective/html
use //$composer require laravelcollective/html


making controller with it resources
$ php artisan make:controller --resource AdminPostsController


then create model and migration using

$  php artisan make:model Post -m

fix table fields and do migrate

$ php artisan migrate

making request, to valideate post inputs

$ php artisan make:request PostCreateRequest


